      "para_id": "Q001688.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) To Nanna , his master , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , dedicated this ( statue ) for his well-being . ... of this statue is \" Nanna is my fortress \"."
    }
